Scenario:
    You are designing a Notification System.

        Based on user preference, you need to send notifications via Email, SMS, or Push.
        The type of notification is not known until runtime.

Practice Task:

    Create an interface Notification with a method notifyUser().

        Concrete classes: EmailNotification, SMSNotification, PushNotification.
        A NotificationFactory class that returns the appropriate object based on input type.